eved <span class=\"nowrap\">17 April</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=CBC+News&amp;rft.atitle=Key+pro-austerity+study+based+on+incorrect+math%3A+Holes+poked+in+analysis+that+claims+high+debt+loads+cause+economies+to+shrink&amp;rft.date=2013-04-17&amp;rft.aulast=Evans&amp;rft.aufirst=Pete&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2F2013%2F04%2F17%2Fbusiness-austerity-rogoff-reinhart.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Herndon\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Trotter_2013-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Trotter_2013_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Trotter_2013_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Trotter, JK. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.theatlanticwire.com/national/2013/04/umass-student-exposes-serious-flaws-harvard-economists-influential-study/64357/\">\"UMass Student Exposes Serious Flaws in Harvard Economists' Influential Study\"</a>. <i>The Atlantic Wire</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.webcitation.org/6HeESIakQ?url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/national/2013/04/umass-student-exposes-serious-flaws-harvard-economists-influential-study/64357/\">Archived</a> from the original on June 25, 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 25,</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Atlantic+Wire&amp;rft.atitle=UMass+Student+Exposes+Serious+Flaws+in+Harvard+Economists%27+Influential+Study&amp;rft.aulast=Trotter&amp;rft.aufirst=JK&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlanticwire.com%2Fnational%2F2013%2F04%2Fumass-student-exposes-serious-flaws-harvard-economists-influential-study%2F64357%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Herndon\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Konczal, Mike (16 April 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/thomas-herndon-michael-ash-and-robert-pollin-on-reinhart-and-rogoff-2013-4\">\"Shocking Paper Claims That Microsoft Excel Coding Error Is Behind The Reinhart-Rogoff Study On Debt\"</a>. <i>Businessinsider</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">16 April</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Businessinsider&amp;rft.atitle=Shocking+Paper+Claims+That+Microsoft+Excel+Coding+Error+Is+Behind+The+Reinhart-Rogoff+Study+On+Debt&amp;rft.date=2013-04-16&amp;rft.aulast=Konczal&amp;rft.aufirst=Mike&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthomas-herndon-michael-ash-and-robert-pollin-on-reinhart-and-rogoff-2013-4&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Herndon\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Parnass, Larry (18 April 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gazettenet.com/home/5775445-95/umass-graduate-student-thomas-herndon-rocks-economics-world-with-class-project-on-debt-growth\">\"UMass graduate student Thomas Herndon rocks economics world with class project on debt, growth\"</a>. <i>Gazettenet</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">18 April</span> 2013</span>.</cit